Invocation Name: odd school schedule
des:
Use this skill to keep track of the class schedule for each student in your household. 

This skill was created using a Skill Blueprint. You can use this in conjunction with Even School Schedule. Disable one and enable the other if your school will swap between Even and Odd starts. Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
